Package com.krobothsoftware.commons.parse

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ExpressionFilter
    Filter applied to HandlerSAX for Expression evaluation.
    ParserHandler
    Parser Listener for handling, and parsing unsupported Handler's.
    ParserInitializable
    Parser can init parsers before they are needed.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultHandlerDelegate
    Delegate DefualtHandler for HandlerSAX implementations.
    Expression
    Limited XPath expression for SAX handler implementations.
    Handler
    Handler to parse data.
    HandlerHtml
    Base Handler for HTML data.
    HandlerHtmlCleaner
    Handler for Html Cleaner types.
    HandlerJson
    Handler for Json types.
    HandlerSAX
    SAX handler for Simple Api for Xml.
    HandlerXml
    Base Handler for XML data.
    Parser
    Parser is used to parse XML and HTML data.
    ParserHtmlCleaner
    Html parser part of SNC-EXT-HTMLCLEANER which parses HandlerHtmlCleaner handlers.
    ParserJson
    Json Parser part of SNC-EXT-JSON which parses HandlerJson handlers.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ParseException
    Parser Exception for parsing data.
    StopException
    Exception for stopping parsing in DefaultHandler which is caught internally.
